  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://www.example.org/ontology/Artemisia#雌花8_12朵花冠狭管状檐部3_2裂齿外面有短柔毛两性花30_50朵孕育或中央若干朵不孕育花冠檐部外面被短柔毛">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.example.org/ontology/Artemisia#花结构与育性"/>
    <rdfs:label>雌花8-12朵，花冠狭管状，檐部3-2裂齿外面有短柔毛；两性花30-50朵，孕育或中央若干朵不孕育，花冠檐部外面被短柔毛</rdfs:label>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://www.example.org/ontology/Artemisia#Artemisia_lactiflora_var_incisa_Pamp_Ling_et_Y_R_Ling">
